A inotify binding for Guile 2.0.

Update
------

* 20120616
  Guile 2.0 compatibility has been tested.
  Now I'm not sure this module fork work for 1.8   :x

* 201206
  Finalize version-1 for guile 1.8 completed.


Notice
------
You should read inotify(7) before using this module for it is
only a stupid wrapper around the original functions.


Trying
------
> touch /tmp/b
> LTDL_LIBRARY_PATH=. guile -L . -s test.scm

and write something to "/tmp/b" to see the program running.
